Description: Elegant & Custom Craftsman at Agate Heights! Adorned with cedar shaker siding, this turn-key residence stuns with lush landscaping & enclosed porch with firepit. Luminous & open floorplan w/ premium finishes, ample natural light, hardwood floors, designer color palette, high-end millwork & multiple cozy fireplaces. Gourmet chef's kitchen w/ high-end appliances, dry bar, huge pantry, & center island w/ eating space. Grab a bottle of wine from impressive lower-level wine cellar & dine al fresco with guests on private deck. Top level dedicated exclusively to primary bedroom w/ vaulted ceilings, fireplace, secret room, & lux bathroom w/ jetted tub. Lower level boasts 2 bedrooms + bonus room & second deck. Pre-inspected & partially furnished.

This solid and well maintained home is ready for you! The long-time owner has decided to hang his hat on being a landlord, but not before spending months of his time and considerable expense in making sure that the turn-key finished product meets his high standards.  A newer roof, new flooring, and fresh paint inside and out just to start. The home has good space with 2 bedrooms on the main level and a large bonus room upstairs, great curb appeal, and it sets in a quiet residential area just 4 minutes away from I-5. The home also has it's own septic, which will save you money on your monthly bills. This is a great home, and an excellent value.

Welcome To Your First Home! Well kept mid-century house makes you feel all cozy and happy.  Nice layout with large living room, bright eating nook and cool kitchen.  Recently refreshed with new carpet and interior paint.  It's absolutely turn-key and includes all appliances.  You'll love that there are two bathrooms, the 1/2 bath has groovy blue porcelain sink and toilet.  Three bedrooms, two with nice built-in drawers. Be sure and check out the unfinished attic above the pull-down staircase-this space is just waiting for you to make it into something special.  Detached garage and fenced back yard.  Close to Skagit County Fairgrounds and walking distance to downtown fun.  Check it out!

This updated country rambler awaits! Located in east Selah, sitting on just over 2 acres of fenced and level land, the possibilities are endless! This home offers 3 full bedroom plus an office/den, along with two and half bathrooms, walk in pantry and more. Updated HVAC, new exterior paint, all updated electrical and new septic system! Don't miss out on this turn-key gem!

*80's Modern* / *Turn-Key* / *4 Bedrooms* / *RV or Boat Parking* / Short jaunt from two of Bellingham's finest offerings: Lake Whatcom & Whatcom Falls Park. A true architectural beauty, your home's anchor is the massive tiled living room with soaring ceilings and a chic loft area. The upper windows both illuminate the home and present eye-popping curb appeal you won't likely see again soon. Experience the open kitchen, the picture window, and the perfect dining room that's ready to feature your unique style. Like the rest of this property, the primary suite denies mundanity and offers a huge space, a walk-in closet, and a large, versatile full bath. The guest wing boasts 3 substantial bedrooms and a full-plus bathroom with multiple closets.

address: 7481 NE North Shore Rd, Belfair, WA 98528
Description: Come enjoy life on saltwater! This large 4 bed home, with lower MIL apt, has 83' on the Hood Canal & offers awesome views. Take in the marine wildlife from your living room or deck, seals and a variety of birds every day, and even the occasional pod of Orcas! Home has been thoughtfully, and fully, remodeled. This beach house is turn-key, and care-free with the updated plumbing and electrical. "Main home" hosts 4 beds, 2.75 baths, an office, & 2 living spaces. All new flooring, paint, kitchen, bathrooms, fixtures, & appliances. Lower level is a BRAND NEW, full 1 bed apt with its own private entrance. Multi-generation? House hack? Air BnB? Spacious 2 car garage with shop has access to both lower level apt, and stairs up to main home.

Whether you're in the market for a sanctuary from everyday life or a turn-key investment property perfectly positioned to take advantage of all Yakima (skiing, wineries, dining, hiking, fishing and YES...a needed respite from the suburban rat race too) has to offer...look no further! Custom built with incredible attention to detail at every turn, this 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 3,526sf log home comes complete with 3 gracious entertaining areas, chef's kitchen, triple pane windows, metal roof, 5+ car garage w shop, additional covered parking and storage and never ending views. Watch the elk and big horn ram while you enjoy coffee from your expansive deck. This one of a kind offering won't last long!

Adorable tiny mountain getaway. Close to Leavenworth, Lake Wenatchee and the town of Plain this is the perfect tiny cabin in the mountains. Located on a residential street makes it easy to access year round while being on a 2.28 acre lot of its own provides the idyllic privacy and quiet for getting away. Inside pine finishes create a warm glow, while a covered deck allows for the perfect nature views. It has been a profitable existing short term rental for 3 years, and currently has a provisional permit from chelan county, could also be a longterm rental or vacation cabin, the opportunities abound. Remodeled in 2017, with the option of all furnishings remain, dont pass up on this turn key opportunity.

Welcome to the Starrett House, 'the Grand Dame', a pivotal Victorian home in Port Townsend. Private home or 'turn-key' B&B business (most antique furnishings included). Built in 1889 by George Starrett for his wife Ann. This home has 11 bedrooms, 10 baths, library, parlor, sitting room & more. A rare free hung staircase rises 70 feet from ground floor to dome. Frescoes of maidens grace the dome. Situated on a corner lot- sited to maximize light & views. Exquisite woodwork, painted high ceilings, period light fixtures & hardware, fire suppression system & fir floors. Close to downtown, shopping, library & beaches. Time-tested brick foundation & sturdy faux slate roof.

Turn key investment with charm and character. Six units with potential to finish basement into two additional apartments.  Well maintained with long term tenants.  Current rents are under market.  Corner lot with large parking lot. Great South Hill locations.  Close to hospitals, parks and schools.  Convenient access to Maple/Ash, Monroe and I-90

Small home that comes with a successful Turn-key auto repair shop AT THE BEACH!  3 bays, all with lifts and equipment necessary to step right in.  Equipment includes alignment machine and drive-on rack, tire machine/balancer, compressor, floor jacks, battery charger, oil holding tanks, security camera system, press, torch with tanks, transmission jack, and much more.  Sale also includes adjacent 2 bedroom/1 bath home.  New septic system installed in 2021. Garage has completely new roof including trusses and sheathing, new electric run thru-out the shop.  Located in the heart of Ocean Park and stays busy all the time.  Time to make the move!

The Annapolis Apartments, a 6-unit trophy asset resting on roughly 0.14 acres of waterfront real estate. Built in 1955, this transit-oriented complex has overseen a complete interior and exterior remodel over the course of ownership (Purchased in 2016). The Annapolis apartments holds 6 1-bedroom 1-bathroom units averaging approximately 695 SF. Constructed with front to back units, all six homes hold unobstructed views of Sinclair Inlet, downtown Bremerton and Bainbridge Island. This fully renovated 6-plex provides investor a rare opportunity to own an irreplaceable turn-key product in Port Orchard’s rapidly growing market.

address: 3928 E Lane Park Rd TRAILER 5, Mead, WA 99021
Description: Evergreen Mobile Home park  14 x 70 in great condition!!  Newer Gas furnace,  On demand hot water, all appliances washer and dryer too!  Septic lines all new!  This unit is turn key and ready to go!  Seller can be out quickly if needed!  All appliances stay!   This wont last!

Turn key income generating property near a high-traffic road with 20,000+ cars driving daily. This 2 acre Property offers a 5bed 2bath Single Family Home with a garage, 3 large shops separately metered with a total of 8 big deep bays (2 are 45'x70' built in 2004 and 1 built in 2017), a studio with full kitchen & bathroom above one of the shops, and 7 connex style storage containers. All units currently rented with long term tenants who are now on a month-to-month providing rental income expandability! Additional storage containers used by owner can be rented out separately. The shops include office areas, lunch rooms, and restrooms. Ample parking, storage and space here offering Excellent opportunity! over 6% CAP close to $100k/yr net!

Popular Southside Walla Walla turn-key winery & home located in 24+ winery cluster w/terrific visitor traffic. Careful planning in design and material is a true example of "form follows function". 7920 sf facility capable of 6000+/- cases, includes climate-controlled (cc) barrel room, cased-goods storage, spacious fermentation area w/glycol delivery, utility, lab, ADA tasting room, 1bed/1bath guest suite w/separate entrance. The 2bed/2bath one-level home features radiant heat, great room w/commercial-style kitchen, massive island, walk-in pantry & wine cellar. Large patio for easy summer living. Brand assets avail. separately. Super location for your winery w/short-term rental opportunities. Water rights. Packet avail on request.

Investor alert! Turn key income property. Rare adjoining 2 parcels at the heart of Capitol Hill (check MLS#1877047). MR Zoning, great potential for upgrade or multi-unit development. Prime location in the coveted neighborhood of Capitol Hill provides easy access to countless restaurants, coffeeshops, shopping, grocery stores, transportation, and entertainment options. Walking distance to the Spheres. This exceptional location coupled with unique house-like living is proven to be very desirable, resulting in higher income and ultra low vacancy.

Opportunity knocks in Wedgewood. Well maintained 4 plex with opportunity. Market rents total $9,100/mo+, =4.4%+ CAP. Two, 2 bedroom / 1 bath flats & Two, 2 bedroom 1.5 bath townhouse units. Units have various updates, full kitchens with dishwashers, keyless entry & mini-split HVAC systems offering energy efficient heat & AC! Coin op laundry room for supplemental income. 7 parking spots. Surrounded by endless amenities, explosive growth & redevelopment. Easy access to Ravenna Ave, Lake City Way, I-5 and just 5 minutes to light rail. Turn key investment opportunity. Current Zone: LR2 (M) offers future value add opportunities.
